            <h3>About PV</h3>
            <p>Born on 10.05.1974 and a resident of Simhachalam, Visakhpatnam ,<b> Mr. Pisini Varanarasimham (PV) </b>identifies himself as a servant of the common man fully dedicated to the cause of Swaraj.</p> <p> A  political leader, philanthropist, revolutionary, writer and much more, held forth on his views even if they went against the popular grain.  Mr. PV straddles several years of experience.  In his personal life PV practices relative simplicity.</p><br>
			
			<p>PV is known to have his own views about various issues plaguing the city and is not afraid of being vocal about them.</p><br>
			
			<p>His popularity amongst the youth especially, is unwavering. PV is also one of the most tech-savvy politicians who created a direct channel with city residents with his facebook and twitter account.and always upheld communal harmony</p><br>
